[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 7234,
        "end_time": 10094,
        "text": "As a wildfire rages through\nthe grasslands,"
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 10094,
        "end_time": 14595,
        "text": "three lions and three wildebeest\nflee for their lives."
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 14595,
        "end_time": 16125,
        "text": "To escape the inferno,"
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 16125,
        "end_time": 21224,
        "text": "they must cross over to the left bank\nof a crocodile-infested river."
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 21224,
        "end_time": 24310,
        "text": "Fortunately, there happens\nto be a raft nearby."
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 24310,
        "end_time": 27488,
        "text": "It can carry up to two animals at a time,"
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 27488,
        "end_time": 30995,
        "text": "and needs as least one lion\nor wildebeest on board"
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 30995,
        "end_time": 33351,
        "text": "to row it across the river."
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 33351,
        "end_time": 35674,
        "text": "There&#39;s just one problem."
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 35674,
        "end_time": 39806,
        "text": "If the lions ever outnumber the\nwildebeest on either side of the river,"
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 39806,
        "end_time": 41444,
        "text": "even for a moment,"
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 41444,
        "end_time": 45426,
        "text": "their instincts will kick in,\nand the results won&#39;t be pretty."
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 45426,
        "end_time": 50075,
        "text": "That includes the animals in the boat\nwhen it&#39;s on a given side of the river."
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 50075,
        "end_time": 54255,
        "text": "What&#39;s the fastest way for all six animals\nto get across"
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 54255,
        "end_time": 57974,
        "text": "without the lions stopping for dinner?"
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 57974,
        "end_time": 61555,
        "text": "Pause here if you want \nto figure it out for yourself."
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 61555,
        "end_time": 62815,
        "text": "Answer in: 3"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 62815,
        "end_time": 63845,
        "text": "Answer in: 2"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 63845,
        "end_time": 64796,
        "text": "Answer in: 1"
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 64796,
        "end_time": 66911,
        "text": "If you feel stuck on a problem like this,"
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 66911,
        "end_time": 70816,
        "text": "try listing all the decisions you can make\nat each point,"
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 70816,
        "end_time": 74195,
        "text": "and the consequences each choice\nleads to."
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 74195,
        "end_time": 78006,
        "text": "For instance, there are five options\nfor who goes across first:"
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 78006,
        "end_time": 79186,
        "text": "one wildebeest,"
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 79186,
        "end_time": 80186,
        "text": "one lion,"
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 80186,
        "end_time": 81286,
        "text": "two wildebeest,"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 81286,
        "end_time": 82275,
        "text": "two lions,"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 82275,
        "end_time": 83736,
        "text": "or one of each."
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 83736,
        "end_time": 85245,
        "text": "If one animal goes alone,"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 85245,
        "end_time": 87587,
        "text": "it&#39;ll just have to come straight back."
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 87587,
        "end_time": 89475,
        "text": "And if two wildebeest cross first,"
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 89475,
        "end_time": 92456,
        "text": "the remaining one will immediately\nget eaten."
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 92456,
        "end_time": 94976,
        "text": "So those options are all out."
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 94976,
        "end_time": 96597,
        "text": "Sending two lions,"
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 96597,
        "end_time": 98267,
        "text": "or one of each animal,"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 98267,
        "end_time": 102506,
        "text": "can actually both lead to solutions\nin the same number of moves."
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 102506,
        "end_time": 105672,
        "text": "For the sake of time,\nwe&#39;ll focus on the second one."
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 105672,
        "end_time": 107637,
        "text": "One of each animal crosses."
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 107637,
        "end_time": 111082,
        "text": "Now, if the wildebeest stays \nand the lion returns,"
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 111082,
        "end_time": 113537,
        "text": "there will be three lions\non the right bank."
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 113537,
        "end_time": 116457,
        "text": "Bad news for the two remaining wildebeest."
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 116457,
        "end_time": 119250,
        "text": "So we need to have the lion\nstay on the left bank"
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 119250,
        "end_time": 121939,
        "text": "and the wildebeest go back to the right."
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 121939,
        "end_time": 123987,
        "text": "Now we have the same five options,"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 123987,
        "end_time": 127137,
        "text": "but with one lion \nalready on the left bank."
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 127137,
        "end_time": 130298,
        "text": "If two wildebeest go,\nthe one that stays will get eaten,"
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 130298,
        "end_time": 132417,
        "text": "and if one of each animal goes,"
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 132417,
        "end_time": 134977,
        "text": "the wildebeest on the raft\nwill be outnumbered"
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 134977,
        "end_time": 137728,
        "text": "as soon as it reaches the other side."
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 137728,
        "end_time": 139078,
        "text": "So that&#39;s a dead end,"
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 139078,
        "end_time": 140978,
        "text": "which means that at the third crossing,"
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 140978,
        "end_time": 143646,
        "text": "only the two lions can go."
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 143646,
        "end_time": 145067,
        "text": "One gets dropped off,"
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 145067,
        "end_time": 147457,
        "text": "leaving two lions on the left bank."
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 147457,
        "end_time": 150457,
        "text": "The third lion takes the raft back to\nthe right bank"
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 150457,
        "end_time": 153018,
        "text": "where the wildebeest are waiting."
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 153018,
        "end_time": 154238,
        "text": "What now?"
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 154238,
        "end_time": 157297,
        "text": "Well, since we&#39;ve got two lions waiting\non the left bank,"
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 157297,
        "end_time": 160877,
        "text": "the only option is for two wildebeest\nto cross."
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 160877,
        "end_time": 164767,
        "text": "Next, there&#39;s no sense in two wildebeest\ngoing back,"
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 164767,
        "end_time": 167339,
        "text": "since that just reverses the last step."
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 167339,
        "end_time": 168909,
        "text": "And if two lions go back,"
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 168909,
        "end_time": 171919,
        "text": "they&#39;ll outnumber the wildebeest\non the right bank."
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 171919,
        "end_time": 175748,
        "text": "So one lion and one wildebeest\ntake the raft back"
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 175748,
        "end_time": 178800,
        "text": "leaving us with one of each animal\non the left bank"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 178800,
        "end_time": 180959,
        "text": "and two of each on the right."
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 180959,
        "end_time": 185149,
        "text": "Again, there&#39;s no point in sending \nthe lion-wildebeest pair back,"
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 185149,
        "end_time": 187981,
        "text": "so the next trip should be either\na pair of lions"
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 187981,
        "end_time": 190098,
        "text": "or a pair of wildebeest."
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 190098,
        "end_time": 193889,
        "text": "If the lions go, they&#39;d eat the wildebeest\non the left, so they stay,"
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 193889,
        "end_time": 196760,
        "text": "and the two wildebeest cross instead."
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 196760,
        "end_time": 200840,
        "text": "Now we&#39;re quite close because the\nwildebeest are all where they need to be"
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 200840,
        "end_time": 202770,
        "text": "with safety in numbers."
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 202770,
        "end_time": 205677,
        "text": "All that&#39;s left is for that one lion\nto raft back"
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 205677,
        "end_time": 209390,
        "text": "and bring his fellow lions over\none by one."
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 209390,
        "end_time": 211589,
        "text": "That makes eleven trips total,"
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 211589,
        "end_time": 215460,
        "text": "the smallest number needed\nto get everyone across safely."
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 215460,
        "end_time": 220062,
        "text": "The solution that involves sending both\nlions on the first step works similarly,"
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 220062,
        "end_time": 223619,
        "text": "and also takes eleven crossings."
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 223619,
        "end_time": 227331,
        "text": "The six animals escape unharmed\nfrom the fire just in time"
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 227331,
        "end_time": 230249,
        "text": "and begin their new lives \nacross the river."
    },
    {
        "index": 82,
        "start_time": 230249,
        "end_time": 232679,
        "text": "Of course, now that the danger&#39;s passed,"
    },
    {
        "index": 83,
        "start_time": 232679,
        "end_time": 237121,
        "text": "it remains to be seen how long their\nunlikely alliance will last."
    }
]